quran[12]{c,v,t}:
  16,15,"Ndipo Iye adakhazikitsa mapiri padziko lapansi kuti lisagwedezeke pamodzi ndi inu, mitsinje ndi misewu kuti mutsogozedwe munjira zabwino"
  16,16,"Ndi zizindikiro zina zokutsogolerani, nyenyezi nazonso anthu amatsogozedwa nazo"
  16,17,Kodi Iye amene amalenga angafanane ndi Iye amene salenga? Kodi inu simungakumbukire
  16,18,Ngati inu mutawerenga zokoma za Mulungu simungakwaniritse kuziwerenga. Ndithudi! Mulungu ndi wokhululukira ndi Mwini chisoni chosatha
  16,19,Ndipo Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene mumabisa ndi zimene mumaonetsera
  16,20,"Koma milungu yabodza imene anthu osakhulupirira amapembedza m’malo mwa Mulungu, siinalenge china chilichonse ayi chifukwa nayonso ndi yolengedwa"
  16,21,"Iyo ndi yakufa, si yamoyo ayi ndiponso iyo siidziwa nthawi imene idzaukitsidwe"
  16,22,"Mulungu wanu ndi Mulungu mmodzi yekha. Koma iwo amene sakhulupirira za m’moyo umene uli nkudza, mitima yawo imakana ndipo iwo ndi odzikweza"
  16,23,"Mosakayika, ndithudi, Mulungu amadziwa zonse zimene iwo amabisa ndi zimene amaonetsera. Ndithudi, Iye sakonda anthu odzikweza"
  16,24,"Pamene amafunsidwa kuti, “Kodi Ambuye wanu wavumbulutsa zotani?” Iwo amati, “Nkhani zopeka za anthu a kalekale.”"
  16,25,Iwo adzanyamula katundu wawo okwanira pa tsiku la kuuka kwa akufa pamodzi ndi katundu wa iwo amene adawasocheretsa mu umbuli. Ndithudi zoipa ndi zimene akusenza
  16,26,Iwo amene adalipo kale adakonza chiwembu koma Mulungu adaphwanya nyumba zawo kuyambira pa maziko ake ndipo denga lidawagwera kuchokera pamwamba pawo ndipo chilango chidadza pa iwo kuchokera ku mbali imene iwo sanali kuganiza